:::Sharpedge/Banzai-Tron:::

::The two Metallica-loving sadists are hanging out and listening to 'Whisky 
in the Jar', all the time singing and banging on their fake guitars::
Both(pretending to sing into the same microphone): 
Mash-a-rain-dum-a-do-dum-a-da!
Whack for my daddy-o! Whack for my daddy-o there's Whisky in the Jar-o!
::As the solo kicks in, they give each other a high five and start drinking 
energon beer by the bottle.  Banzai-Tron passes out after a bit, but 
Sharpedge keeps going.  Eventually the large quantities of energon make him 
overload and pass out. But as he lay on the floor, something strange started 
happening to his body......::
